# vs [![Build Status](https://secure.travis-ci.org/tknew/vs.png?branch=master)](http://travis-ci.org/tknew/vs)

The best project ever.

## Getting Started
Install the module with: `npm install vs`

```javascript
var vs = require('vs');
console.log(vs.hello());
```
